p.k: Dr. Fox is proud to unveil her new ultimate combat machine. / Unikitty finds an old, beatup recliner on the curb, but sees its inner beauty and brings it home to introduce to the gang! / Puppycorn wants to impress his skater friends with his sweet skills, except he has none. / Unikitty and Hawkodile are "lost at sea", stranded on a raft together... / When Unikitty has a little auto incident with Master Frown, he insists on taking it to court! Frown's thrilled.
